  "text": "We used EM3D to calculate and render a surface model for each VOI. The calculation was done using a gray scale value that minimized the mean spatial uncertainty averaged across the whole area of the model. Surface models generated in this way had a spatial resolution equal to the resolution of the reconstructed volumes [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] .",
